pref-dialog-open-shortcut-key-label = Dialog Open Shortcut Key

pref-dialog-open-shortcut-key-description = Provides a keyboard shortcut to open the dialog.<br/>
    Supported shortcuts include:<br/>
    - Function keys (e.g. F1, F2)<br/>
    - Modifier key combinations (e.g. Ctrl+Alt+D)<br/><br/>

    Format: Modifier+Key (e.g. Ctrl+Shift+K).<br/>
    Modifiers: Ctrl, Alt, Shift, Meta (Command on macOS).<br/><br/>

    Note: Currently only Ctrl modifier has been thoroughly tested.<br/>
    Other modifiers may not work as expected.<br/>
    Please restart Zotero after configuration.

